localed: localed (locale daemon for org.freedesktop.locale1)
localed:
localed: localed is a system service that manages the system locale and
localed: keyboard configuration. It implements the
localed: org.freedesktop.locale1 D-Bus interface as a drop-in
localed: replacement for systemd-localed on systems without systemd.
localed:
localed: It supports PolKit authentication and manages locale.conf,
localed: vconsole.conf, and X11 keyboard layout configuration.
